254:  Each Forge run records per-library metrics under `stats/<group>/<artifact>/<version>/execution-metrics.json` and, when invoked through `git_scripts/make_pr_*.py`, opens a PR ready for human review. See [forge/README.md](../forge/README.md) and [forge/docs/functional-spec.md](../forge/docs/functional-spec.md).
